name: Shiboki
description: SHIBOKI is a mixed breed dog that is on a mission to prove to his parents “Shiba” & “Floki” that he will carry on with their legacies and that his name is destined for greatness as well. How is he planning on doing so? He built a team around him which consisted of a Solidity Developer, a hard working Co-founder, and a Creative Designer. The team put a plan to lead the community and achieve SHIBOKI’s goals.
